## 關於訓練資料 (About Training Data)

本模型訓練於 **POP909 Dataset**，該資料集僅授權用於非商業及學術研究用途。
若您將本專案用於任何商業目的，請確認您所使用的訓練資料符合其原始授權條款。

The model was trained on the **POP909 Dataset**, which is licensed for non-commercial and academic research use only.
If you use this project for any commercial purpose, please ensure your training data complies with its original license terms.
